                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Barcelona</placeName>\n                                        <date>Janry 18th/53</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Is Leeser Esqr.</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <placeName>Philadpa</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Revd. Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Your valued note of the <date>15<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                                                  >th</hi></date> ulto. was recd &amp; duly\n                                        no<lb/>ticed together with the proof sheet, the size of\n                                        which, is more porta<lb/>ble than those your last edition,\n                                        excepting the quality of paper, which<lb/> I found to be a\n                                        little inferior; my subscribers, thro' my organ,<lb/> begs\n                                        to have equal quality as the set of Parasa &amp; Prayer<lb/>\n                                        Books which I hold here of your first Edition, that is,\n                                        “with<lb/> no additional cost.”</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am truly sorry that I cannot prove of more<lb/>\n                                        service to yr valued Periodical the Occident &amp; moreso to\n                                        feel<lb/> the justice of your observation; for tho' few, we\n                                        (they) feel very<lb/> little interest in the genl. cause of\n                                        Judaism—As far<lb/> as concerns myself, I doubt not you will\n                                        send or continue<lb/> sending the nos. &amp; inform me thro\n                                        what channel you would<lb/> like them import to be remitted\n                                        to you—<sic>wether</sic> Lag<add>?</add><lb/> or\n                                                  <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>.<add>?</add>\n                                        Revd. Sr. I remain</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">respectfully yours,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Saml Piza</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>P.S. Please stamp no name on the covers of the set orderd<lb/> for\n                                                  <persName>A. H. Moro</persName>.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3bk17927/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
